longBusinessSummary: JPO Solutions, Inc. produces and supplies absorbents, primarily for the oil, gas, and chemical industries. It offers organic and biodegradeable absorbents for petroleum based liquid, absorbents for use on water, absorbents for various liquids, and absorbent pads, pillows, socks, and spill kits. The company was formerly known as MOP Environmental Solutions, Inc. and changed its name to JPO Solutions, Inc. in August 2015. JPO Solutions, Inc. was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Fairfield, Connecticut.
